text: Þis synt þa land gemæro to wiþilea.
Of þam forda on gerihte to þam smalan wege.
Forð on þone weg to poddan beorge.
Of þam beorge to wiþig slæde.
Of þam slæde on gerihte to brocenan beorge.
Of þam beorge to wudu forda, of þam forda on gerihte to lulles beorge.
Of þam beorge forð andlang herpoþes to cynulfes treowe.
Of þam treowe on gerihte to mægen stanes dene.
Of þære dene on þone weg to wiþilea gate.
Of þam gate forð be þære dic eft to ucing forda.
Þis is þæra feower hyda land boc æt Wiþiglea þe Eadgar cing hæfð gebocod Cenulfe on ece yrfe.
